Package: slabR
Type: Package
Title: Summarise slabs from arrays in R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jack H",
           family = "Laverick",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jacklaverick@ymail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8829-2084"))
Maintainer: Jack H Laverick <jacklaverick@ymail.com>
Description: A package for creating summary slabs from arrays according to a summary scheme. This is useful for ecosystem models which use a single value to represent volumes within a 3D grid. The different summaries are implemented in C++ using Rcpp for speed.
